"This is the name which will be used on the Equities Tab. You will also be "
"asked to specify the type of investment. The currently available values are "
"Stock, Bond, and Mutual Fund. If your investment is not strictly one of "
"these types, it is ok to mislabel here, as the type is not currently used to "
"restrict or control what you can do with the investment."
msgstr ""

