msgid ""
"There are two ways of updating the prices for your investments. You can "
"either enter the price manually or have &kmymoney; fetch it from the web."
msgstr ""
"Postoje dva načina za ažuriranje cijena za vašu investiciju. Možete ili "
"unijeti cijenu ručno ili je može &kappname; dobaviti sa interneta."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual Price Updates"
msgstr "Ručna ažuriranja cijena"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter prices for your investments using the same <link linkend="
"\"details.currencies.prices\">Price Editor</link> as used for currencies."
msgstr ""
"Možete unijeti cijene za svoje investicije upotrebom istog <link linkend="
"\"details.currencies.prices\">Price Editor</link> kao i za valute."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Price Quotes"
msgstr "Online navodi cijena"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:805
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; has the ability to download the latest prices for your "
#| "investments and currencies via the web."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has the ability to download the latest prices for your securities "
"and currencies via the web."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; ima mogućnost da downloaduje najnovije cijene za vaše investicije "
"i valute pomoću interneta."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid "How Online Quotes Work"
msgstr "Kako online navodi rade"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:811
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "At your request, &kappname; will fetch a page from the web that contains "
#| "the latest price for each item. By default, prices are fetched from "
#| "<ulink url=\"http://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>, and "
#| "are subject to the terms and conditions of that site."
msgid ""
"At your request, &kmymoney; will fetch a page from the web that contains the "
"latest price for each security. By default, prices are fetched from <ulink "
"url=\"https://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>, and are subject "
"to the terms and conditions of that site."
msgstr ""
"Po vašem zahtjevu, &kappname; če dobaviti stranicu sa interneta koja sadrži "
"najnovije cijene za svaku stavku. Kao što je unaprijed definisano, cijene se "
"dobavljaju sa <ulink url=\"http://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</"
"ulink> i u skladu su sa uvjetima te stranice."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:818
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The online quote lookup uses the investment's trading symbol to find the "
#| "price. Therefore, it's important to set the symbol correctly. Yahoo "
#| "supports stocks from most major world markets, so it's usually just a "
#| "matter of finding the correct symbol. For example, TietoEnator trades on "
#| "the Stockholm Stock Exchange market, and its Yahoo symbol is TIEN.ST."
msgid ""
"The online quote lookup uses the security's trading symbol to find the "
"price. Therefore, it is important to set the symbol correctly. Yahoo "
"supports stocks from most major world markets, so it is usually just a "
"matter of finding the correct symbol. For example, TietoEnator trades on the "
"Stockholm Stock Exchange market, and its Yahoo symbol is TIEN.ST."
msgstr ""
"Pretraživač online navoda koristi simbol trgovanja investicije da bi "
"pronašao cijene. Zato je potrebno da se simbol postavi korektno. Yahoo "
"podržava dionice sa većine glavnih svjetskih tržišta, pa je često samo "
"pitanje pronalaska pravog simbola. Npr., TietoEnator trguje na Stockholm "
"Stock Exchange tržištu i njegov Yahoo simbol je TIEN.ST."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:826
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To find the trading symbol for a security supported by Yahoo, use the "
#| "<quote>Symbol Lookup</quote> feature at <ulink url=\"http://finance.yahoo."
#| "com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>."
msgid ""
"To find the trading symbol for a security supported by Yahoo, use the "
"<quote>Symbol Lookup</quote> feature at <ulink url=\"https://finance.yahoo."
"com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>. You should have set the trading symbol when "
"initially entering the security into &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Da biste pronašli simbol pomoću kojeg se trguje podržan od Yahoo-a, "
"koristite <quote>Symbol Lookup</quote> opciju na <ulink url=\"http://finance."
"yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assigning a Quote Source"
msgstr "Dodjela izvora navoda"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:835
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In order to get online price quotes, you first have to enable it for each "
#| "investment or currency you want updated, by setting a <quote>Online Quote "
#| "Source</quote>. This is the name of the service from which the quote "
#| "should be fetched. &kappname; ships with several sources to choose from. "
#| "Yahoo is the recommended default source, and should work for most "
#| "investments and all currencies."
msgid ""
"In order to get online price quotes, you first have to enable the feature "
"for each security or currency you want updated, by setting an <quote>Online "
"Quote Source</quote>. This is the name of the service from which the quote "
"should be fetched. &kmymoney; ships with several sources to choose from. "
"Yahoo is the recommended default source, and should work for most "
"investments and all currencies."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dobili navode online cijena, prvo to morate omogućiti za svaku "
"investiciju ili valutu za koju želite ažuriranje, pomoću postavljanja "
"<quote>Online Quote Source</quote>. Ovo je ime servisa sa kojeg bi se navod "
"trebao dobaviti. &kappname; vam donosi nekoliko izbora između kojih možete "
"birati. Yahoo je preporučeni unaprijed definisani izvor i trebao bi raditi "
"za većinu investicija i za sve valute."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:844
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To assign a quote source to an investment, navigate to the investment "
#| "summary view for the account in which the security is held. Edit the "
#| "security by right-clicking it and selecting <guimenuitem>Edit "
#| "Investment ...</guimenuitem>. In the Investment Detail Wizard, click "
#| "<guibutton>Next</guibutton> twice, for the Online Update section. In the "
#| "Online source dropdown box, select the online source."
msgid ""
"To assign a quote source for an investment, navigate to the investment "
"summary view for the account in which the security is held. Edit the "
"security by right-clicking it and selecting <guimenuitem>Edit Investment ..."
"</guimenuitem>. In the Investment Detail Wizard, click <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> twice, for the Online Update section. In the Online source "
"dropdown box, select the online source for your needs."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dodijelili izvor navoda investiciji, otiđite na sumarni pregled "
"investicija za račun u kojem se nalazi sigurnost. Editujte sigurnost desnim "
"klikom na nju i odabirom <guimenuitem>Edit Investment ...</guimenuitem>. U "
"čarobnjaku detalja investicije, kliknite na <guibutton>Next</guibutton> dva "
"puta, za sekciju online ažuriranja. U opadajućem prostori online izvora, "
"odaberite jedan online izvor."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:853
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Versions of &kappname; starting with 0.9 contain support for the Finance::"
#| "Quote package for obtaining online quotes. This is intended primarily as "
#| "a convenience for those users converting from the GnuCash finance "
#| "package, which uses it as its native method. If you do select this "
#| "option, you should see a different list of sources, those supported by "
#| "Finance::Quote. If the list is empty, it suggests that the package is not "
#| "properly installed. See their web site at <ulink url=\"http://finance-"
#| "quote.sourceforge.net\"> http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net</ulink> for "
#| "more information."
msgid ""
"Versions of &kmymoney; starting with 0.9 contain support for the Perl "
"Finance::Quote package for obtaining online quotes. This is intended "
"primarily as a convenience for those users converting from the &gnucash; "
"finance package, which uses it as its native method. If you do select this "
"option, you should see a different list of sources, those supported by "
"Finance::Quote. If the list is empty, it suggests that the package is not "
"properly installed. See their web site at <ulink url=\"http://finance-quote."
"sourceforge.net\"> http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Verzije &kappname; počevši od 0.9 sadrže podršku za Finansije::Navod paket "
"za dobivanje online navoda. Ovo je primarno namijenjeno kao pogodnost za one "
"korisnike koji konvertuju iz GnuCash finansijskog paketa koji ovo koristi "
"kao urođenu metodu. Ukoliko odaberete ovu opciju, treali biste vidjeti "
"različitu listu izvora, one podržane od strane Finansija::Navod. Ukoliko je "
"lista prazna, vjerovatno paket nije pravilno instaliran. Pogledajte njihovu "
"internet stranicu na <ulink url=\"http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net\"> "
"http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net</ulink> za više informacija."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjusting a quote"
msgstr "Podešavanje navoda"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:866
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Some online sources do not report the price in a base quantity (&eg;, "
#| "EUR) but in a fraction (&eg;, Cent). Using this information as price will "
#| "produce wrong values for your investments."
msgid ""
"Some online sources do not report the price in a base quantity (&eg;, EUR) "
"but in a fraction (&eg;, Cent). Using this information for a price will "
"produce wrong values for your investments."
msgstr ""
"Neki online izvori ne prijavljuju cijenu u baznoj količini (&eg;, EUR) već u "
"frakciji (&eg;, Cent). Upotreba ove informacije kao cijene će proizvesti "
"pogrešne vrijednosti za vaše investicije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is the case for your online source, you can use the "
"<guilabel>Factor</guilabel> field to enter an adjusting factor. For the "
"above mentioned example the factor would be 0.01."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko je ovo slulčaj sa vašim online izvorom, možete upotrijebiti "
"<guilabel>Factor</guilabel> polje da unesete podešavajući faktor. Za gore "
"navedeni primjer, on bi bio 0.01."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Factor</guilabel> field is only available if a "
"<guibutton>Quote Source</guibutton> has been selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Faktor</guilabel> polje je omogućeno samo ako je <guibutton>Izvor "
"navoda</guibutton> selektirano."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fetching Quotes"
msgstr "Dobavljanje navoda"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:885
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Typically, you will update the prices for all your investments and "
#| "currencies at once. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
